Description: Nautilus extension for resizing images with right-click menu
 A context menu extension for Nautilus file manager that allows
 users to resize images through a simple GUI interface.
 .
 Features:
  * Right-click integration in Nautilus
  * Multiple resize options and presets
  * Aspect ratio locking
  * Format conversion support
  * Modern GTK4 interface